Titolo: Crazy Cars: Hit the Road

Anno: 2012

Descrizione: Crazy Cars: Hit the Road is a video game published by Anuman under their Microïds brand and developed by Little World Entertainment. Microïds was granted the license by Interplay Entertainment, who would subsequently begin promoting the game as well. The game, based on a former property owned by Titus Interactive, features free play and career mode in an arcade-based experience. Available for PC, iOS and Android, the game was released on October 15, 2012.